22
00:01:35,804 --> 00:01:37,389
<i>Dikurung karena membuat masalah.</i>

23
00:01:38,307 --> 00:01:40,684
<i>Kekerasan terhadap anak! Pelanggaran HAM!</i>

24
00:01:40,768 --> 00:01:42,478
<i>Kandidat Kwon Man-su harus mundur!</i>

25
00:01:42,561 --> 00:01:45,648
<i>- Mundur!
- Segera setelah insiden tersebut,</i>

26
00:01:45,731 --> 00:01:48,734
<i>publik menyerukan agar Kandidat Kwon</i>

27
00:01:48,817 --> 00:01:52,196
<i>- mengundurkan diri secara sukarela.</i>
- Dia bisa kehilangan jabatannya.

28
00:01:52,279 --> 00:01:55,240
<i>- Penting memiliki keutuhan rumah tangga.</i>
- Bagaimana Penulis Ko?

29
00:01:55,324 --> 00:01:57,368
<i>- Ayah kejam seperti dia</i>
- Dia yang memulai.

30
00:01:57,451 --> 00:02:00,454
<i>- apa bisa mengurus keluarga orang lain</i>
- Entahlah. Bagaimana?

31
00:02:00,537 --> 00:02:01,914
<i>dan mengurus negara ini?</i>

32
00:02:02,956 --> 00:02:04,958
<i>Kandidat Kwon harus mengundurkan diri!</i>

33
00:02:10,422 --> 00:02:15,677
<font color="#00ff00">BAB 4
KISAH HIDUP ZOMBI</font>

34
00:02:15,803 --> 00:02:19,139
<i>Lihatlah aku</i>

35
00:02:19,223 --> 00:02:22,142
- Ambil mikrofonnya!
<i>- Kandidat nomor satu</i>

36
00:02:22,226 --> 00:02:23,644
<font color="#00ff00">3 JAM LALU</font>

37
00:02:24,561 --> 00:02:27,147
- Cepat!
- Astaga.

38
00:02:27,439 --> 00:02:28,774
- Lihat dia.
- Astaga.

39
00:02:29,274 --> 00:02:30,192
Mau bermain apa?

40
00:02:33,153 --> 00:02:34,822
Mau ke mana? Katanya mau bermain?

41
00:02:34,905 --> 00:02:35,823
Kapan aku mau?

42
00:02:36,907 --> 00:02:38,200
Kau mengidap mitomania?

43
00:02:40,035 --> 00:02:41,412
Ucapanku tadi...

44
00:02:42,996 --> 00:02:44,206
Aku hanya bicara sendiri.

45
00:02:45,541 --> 00:02:47,167
Puji aku karena berbuat baik.

46
00:02:47,251 --> 00:02:48,877
- Untuk apa?
- Penculikan.

47
00:02:50,045 --> 00:02:51,922
Kau tidak menghentikan, tapi membiarkan.

48
00:02:52,005 --> 00:02:53,465
Itu karena perbuatanku benar.

49
00:02:54,758 --> 00:02:55,592
Bukan begitu?

50
00:02:56,176 --> 00:02:57,386
Kenapa tak dihentikan?

51
00:03:01,098 --> 00:03:02,808
Mana bisa kuhentikan

52
00:03:03,392 --> 00:03:04,435
saat dia tampil bagus?

53
00:03:09,314 --> 00:03:10,315
Permisi!

54
00:03:13,694 --> 00:03:15,738
Siapa kalian? Apa staf rumah sakit?

55
00:03:15,821 --> 00:03:18,532
Bukan. Aku seorang penulis.
Dia tuas pengamanku.

56
00:03:20,033 --> 00:03:23,787
Jika kejadian buruk sampai menimpa
Anggota Dewan Kwon...

57
00:03:23,871 --> 00:03:24,830
Lantas apa?

58
00:03:26,623 --> 00:03:28,041
Persiapkan diri kalian.

59
00:03:29,084 --> 00:03:31,086
Astaga. Begitu? Menakutkan.

60
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:33,464
- Aku takut. Bagaimana ini?
- Kau...

61
00:03:36,341 --> 00:03:37,551
Jaga tanganmu.

62
00:03:40,387 --> 00:03:43,140
Kalian telah melakukan kesalahan besar!

63
00:03:43,724 --> 00:03:44,600
Bersiaplah!

64
00:03:47,853 --> 00:03:50,189
Kenapa terus menggertak? Dasar bajingan.

65
00:03:58,155 --> 00:04:00,407
Gang-tae, Gi-do mencarimu.

66
00:04:03,952 --> 00:04:05,162
Kau sudah bekerja keras.

67
00:04:09,541 --> 00:04:10,959
Diam di sini.

68
00:04:15,881 --> 00:04:17,090
Ayo.

69
00:04:17,257 --> 00:04:20,177
Terima kasih sudah membantu kami
meskipun kalian sedang sibuk.

70
00:04:25,349 --> 00:04:26,183
Gang-tae.

71
00:04:28,852 --> 00:04:30,604
Keinginanku terwujud semua.

72
00:04:33,774 --> 00:04:35,484
Ini hari terindah di hidupku.

73
00:04:36,235 --> 00:04:39,863
Jadi, jangan marahi dia
karena membawaku kemari.

74
00:04:42,658 --> 00:04:43,492
Ya?

75
00:04:50,457 --> 00:04:51,834
- Ibu, tenanglah.
- Astaga.

76
00:04:51,917 --> 00:04:53,293
- Ibu.
- Dia sudah aman.

77
00:04:53,961 --> 00:04:57,798
Permisi, salah satu anggota keluarga
harus ikut kami ke RSJ.

78
00:04:57,881 --> 00:04:59,258
Kau sudah gila?

79
00:04:59,633 --> 00:05:01,635
Kenapa kami harus pergi ke RSJ?

80
00:05:03,220 --> 00:05:06,348
Kalian pergilah temani ayah kalian.

81
00:05:07,015 --> 00:05:07,933
Ibu.

82
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,644
Ibu!

83
00:05:13,105 --> 00:05:14,106
Gi-do.

84
00:05:16,858 --> 00:05:18,318
Ibu. Aku sudah membaik...

85
00:05:20,404 --> 00:05:23,865
Apa kau sudah lega setelah mempermalukan
keluarga kita di depan umum?

86
00:05:24,741 --> 00:05:28,245
Setelah mempermalukan ayahmu
yang paling kau benci,

87
00:05:29,329 --> 00:05:30,956
kau merasa puas?

88
00:05:32,332 --> 00:05:33,625
Ibu, aku hanya...

89
00:05:33,917 --> 00:05:36,628
Kenapa kau harus lahir dari perutku

90
00:05:38,130 --> 00:05:41,133
dengan penuh kekurangan dan dilecehkan?

91
00:05:41,925 --> 00:05:43,844
Kenapa kau selalu bertingkah

92
00:05:44,052 --> 00:05:46,221
dan menghancurkan hatiku?

93
00:05:46,305 --> 00:05:48,599
Seharusnya kau pura-pura mati saja!

94
00:05:48,682 --> 00:05:50,767
Kenapa kau terus membawa masalah

95
00:05:51,351 --> 00:05:54,938
dan membuat keributan, dasar bodoh!

96
00:05:56,148 --> 00:05:57,316
Kenapa?

97
00:06:24,968 --> 00:06:26,511
Tamparan ibuku perih sekali.

98
00:06:30,557 --> 00:06:32,184
Ibu bahkan tak peduli denganku.

99
00:06:32,267 --> 00:06:34,603
Hanya memperhatikan kakak-kakakku.

100
00:06:39,316 --> 00:06:41,526
Setelah ditampar, aku bisa merasakannya.

101
00:06:42,653 --> 00:06:43,654
Gang-tae.

102
00:06:45,656 --> 00:06:47,366
Ibuku tak membenciku.

103
00:06:48,283 --> 00:06:49,618
Dia sangat menyayangiku.

104
00:06:52,746 --> 00:06:53,872
Bagaimana bisa tahu?

105
00:06:55,165 --> 00:06:56,875
Orang yang kena pukul bisa merasakan.

106
00:06:58,502 --> 00:07:01,421
Anehnya, saat dipukul
dengan penuh kasih sayang,

107
00:07:02,881 --> 00:07:04,633
kau tidak merasa kesal sedikit pun.

108
00:07:09,429 --> 00:07:10,555
<i>Moon Gang-tae!</i>

109
00:07:12,224 --> 00:07:15,143
Kenapa begitu?
Kenapa Sang-tae pulang sendiri?

110
00:07:15,227 --> 00:07:17,562
Seharusnya kau menjaganya!

111
00:07:18,605 --> 00:07:20,524
Apa yang kau lakukan saat dia dipukuli?

112
00:07:20,982 --> 00:07:23,485
Kau boleh belajar bela diri
untuk menjaga kakakmu.

113
00:07:23,568 --> 00:07:25,487
Kenapa kau membiarkannya dipukuli?

114
00:07:27,698 --> 00:07:28,532
Kenapa?

115
00:07:29,658 --> 00:07:31,535
Astaga. Hujannya deras sekali.

116
00:07:34,496 --> 00:07:36,456
Jangan sampai pilek. Kau tak apa-apa?

117
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:51,304
Suamiku.

118
00:07:52,681 --> 00:07:54,516
Aku takkan mati muda sepertimu.

119
00:07:56,435 --> 00:07:58,520
Umurku akan panjang.

120
00:07:59,980 --> 00:08:03,692
Aku ingin melihat Sang-tae hidup tua
sampai meninggal.

121
00:08:05,110 --> 00:08:08,030
Keesokan harinya, aku akan mati
mengikuti Sang-tae.

122
00:08:19,082 --> 00:08:19,916
Ibu?

123
00:08:23,462 --> 00:08:26,590
Astaga. Anakku terbangun?

124
00:08:32,637 --> 00:08:34,639
- Gang-tae.
- Ya?

125
00:08:35,223 --> 00:08:37,893
Kau harus terus menjaga kakakmu
hingga ajal menjemput.

126
00:08:41,313 --> 00:08:43,440
Ibu akan membesarkannya.

127
00:08:44,316 --> 00:08:47,694
Kau hanya perlu melindungi dan menjaganya.

128
00:08:48,445 --> 00:08:49,404
Mengerti?

129
00:08:56,078 --> 00:08:57,454
Itu sebabnya

130
00:08:59,122 --> 00:09:01,166
ibu melahirkanmu.

131
00:09:18,642 --> 00:09:19,851
<font color="#00ff00">RUMAH SAKIT JIWA OK</font>

132
00:09:24,898 --> 00:09:26,274
Kita harus pergi juga.

133
00:09:29,444 --> 00:09:30,278
Ju-ri.

134
00:09:35,951 --> 00:09:38,537
- Kita pergi.
- Pergi bermain?

135
00:09:39,412 --> 00:09:40,580
Kita ke rumah sakit.

136
00:09:41,498 --> 00:09:42,749
Jangan mengebut.

137
00:09:59,099 --> 00:10:01,393
Ju-ri. Pergi saja tanpaku.

138
00:10:02,227 --> 00:10:03,812
Aku akan naik mobil itu.

139
00:10:09,109 --> 00:10:09,943
Kenapa?

140
00:10:10,819 --> 00:10:11,695
Aku merasa...

141
00:10:16,324 --> 00:10:17,784
dia tak boleh menyetir sendiri.

142
00:10:37,053 --> 00:10:38,388
Jika kau tak naik mobilku,

143
00:10:40,015 --> 00:10:41,683
aku berniat untuk menculikmu.

144
00:10:43,810 --> 00:10:45,270
Apa itu hobimu?

145
00:10:45,979 --> 00:10:48,481
Kau pasti iri melihat si Burung Kecil
bersenang-senang.

146
00:10:49,566 --> 00:10:53,069
"Aku juga ingin bersenang-senang begitu."

147
00:10:53,945 --> 00:10:55,614
Tertulis jelas di raut wajahmu.

148
00:10:57,657 --> 00:10:58,992
Saat siap, katakan saja.

149
00:10:59,409 --> 00:11:02,203
Aku akan menculikmu
dan membuatmu menikmati hidup.

150
00:11:02,287 --> 00:11:03,872
Pasti luar biasa.

151
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,878
Lupakan saja.

152
00:11:11,046 --> 00:11:14,090
Baiklah. Saat kau terlihat
ingin melarikan diri,

153
00:11:14,925 --> 00:11:17,135
aku akan melarikan diri bersamamu.

154
00:11:17,969 --> 00:11:19,012
Lihat saja nanti.

155
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,083
Sial.

156
00:11:48,166 --> 00:11:51,544
Aku paling benci serpihan bunga kecil
yang berjatuhan seperti ini.

157
00:11:58,802 --> 00:12:00,178
Aku suka magnolia.

158
00:12:00,762 --> 00:12:03,014
Seluruh kelopaknya gugur sekaligus
tanpa ragu.

159
00:12:03,098 --> 00:12:04,265
Itulah yang kusuka.

160
00:12:08,144 --> 00:12:10,772
Caramu membuat perbandingan selalu...

161
00:12:10,855 --> 00:12:12,565
Selalu cantik, bukan?

162
00:12:17,112 --> 00:12:19,656
Ya. Bunga magnolia cocok denganmu.

163
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,741
Kau suka bunga apa?

164
00:12:24,494 --> 00:12:25,453
Aku tak suka.

165
00:12:27,622 --> 00:12:29,207
Aku benci musim semi.

166
00:12:30,792 --> 00:12:31,626
Kenapa?

167
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:38,299
Karena harus pindah lagi.

168
00:12:40,051 --> 00:12:40,885
Apa?

169
00:13:23,928 --> 00:13:25,263
Pak Lee.

170
00:13:25,346 --> 00:13:26,848
Ya. Bagaimana?

171
00:13:27,599 --> 00:13:30,226
Larangan penjualan buku <i>Kisah Hidup Zombi</i>

172
00:13:30,310 --> 00:13:31,603
telah disetujui, Pak.

173
00:13:34,731 --> 00:13:36,608
Begitu.

174
00:13:37,859 --> 00:13:41,654
Berarti kita hanya perlu
mengembalikan semuanya?

175
00:13:41,780 --> 00:13:42,614
Ya.

176
00:13:43,615 --> 00:13:44,449
Menurutmu lucu?

177
00:13:45,158 --> 00:13:46,743
Kau bisa tertawa?

178
00:13:47,243 --> 00:13:49,496
Perusahaan terancam bangkrut
dan kau bisa tertawa?

179
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:53,458
Lalu apa aku harus menangis?

180
00:13:53,541 --> 00:13:54,459
Tidak.

181
00:13:55,460 --> 00:13:56,294
Kau keluar saja.

182
00:13:56,878 --> 00:13:59,047
Cepat tulis surat pengunduran diri
dan pergi.

183
00:14:13,561 --> 00:14:14,396
<i>Akhirnya</i>

184
00:14:15,355 --> 00:14:18,149
<i>aku menemukan sepatu merahku.</i>

185
00:14:27,242 --> 00:14:28,326
<font color="#00ff00">RIWAYAT HIDUP GANG-TAE</font>

186
00:14:33,498 --> 00:14:35,125
Pak Lee. Kau mau minum kopi?

187
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,127
Mau ke mana?

188
00:14:38,211 --> 00:14:39,337
Urusan bisnis!

189
00:14:40,588 --> 00:14:41,714
Hati-hati di jalan.

190
00:14:47,262 --> 00:14:48,096
Hore!

191
00:14:59,774 --> 00:15:02,068
Aku mengajakmu makan.
Kenapa malah ke sini?

192
00:15:02,152 --> 00:15:03,570
Cepat makan. Aku harus kerja.

193
00:15:05,029 --> 00:15:07,282
- Mau kubelikan nasi kepal?
- Tidak perlu.

194
00:15:12,787 --> 00:15:13,788
Ya?

195
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:16,374
Tunggu sebentar.

196
00:15:17,792 --> 00:15:18,710
Makanlah.

197
00:15:25,508 --> 00:15:27,927
Sial. Tak ada kimchi.

198
00:15:28,011 --> 00:15:29,554
Dia benar-benar pelit.

199
00:15:30,096 --> 00:15:31,890
Tak masalah miskin, tapi jangan pelit.

200
00:15:31,973 --> 00:15:33,266
Kenapa meneleponku?

201
00:15:33,391 --> 00:15:35,393
<i>Apa keadaan terkendali?</i>

202
00:15:35,476 --> 00:15:36,311
Apa?

203
00:15:37,395 --> 00:15:38,480
Baguslah.

204
00:15:40,482 --> 00:15:41,357
Apa maksudnya?

205
00:15:43,318 --> 00:15:44,277
Sial.

206
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:46,905
<i>Pak Moon. Aku bertanya
hanya untuk berjaga-jaga.</i>

207
00:15:46,988 --> 00:15:49,866
Apa Penulis Ko pernah mengatakan sesuatu

208
00:15:50,241 --> 00:15:54,662
bahwa kau cantik, dia menginginkanmu,
atau perkataan serupa itu?

209
00:15:56,247 --> 00:15:58,166
<i>- Kenapa aku?</i>
- Aku terus menginginkanmu.

210
00:15:58,666 --> 00:16:00,668
- Apa alasannya?
- Karena kau cantik.

211
00:16:04,172 --> 00:16:05,632
Dia pasti bilang begitu.

212
00:16:06,799 --> 00:16:07,759
Memangnya kenapa?

213
00:16:08,426 --> 00:16:10,929
Dengarkan aku baik-baik.

214
00:16:11,012 --> 00:16:13,181
Saat dia bilang menginginkanmu,

215
00:16:13,264 --> 00:16:15,642
sama artinya dia sedang lapar.

216
00:16:16,434 --> 00:16:20,855
<i>Dengan kata lain,
dia akan melahapmu hidup-hidup.</i>

217
00:16:24,484 --> 00:16:25,610
Lalu?

218
00:16:25,693 --> 00:16:30,114
Kita sedang dalam keadaan
yang sangat darurat.

219
00:16:30,490 --> 00:16:32,951
<i>Buku terbarunya dilarang beredar,</i>

220
00:16:33,034 --> 00:16:36,371
<i>dia tak seharusnya
bersantai bersamamu di sana.</i>

221
00:16:36,454 --> 00:16:38,039
<i>Dia harus menulis buku baru.</i>

222
00:16:41,751 --> 00:16:42,919
Pundaknya bidang sekali.

223
00:16:47,799 --> 00:16:50,927
<i>Apa pun yang terjadi, aku akan
menyeretnya kembali ke Seoul.</i>

224
00:16:51,010 --> 00:16:53,471
<i>Tolong tetap hidup sampai... Maksudku...</i>

225
00:16:54,055 --> 00:16:56,391
Kau harus bertahan sampai saat itu.

226
00:16:57,308 --> 00:16:58,518
Semoga beruntung.

227
00:17:10,655 --> 00:17:11,656
Siapa?

228
00:17:13,283 --> 00:17:15,159
- Rumah sakit.
- Mereka memintamu kembali?

229
00:17:16,119 --> 00:17:17,287
Atau mau memecatku?

230
00:17:19,497 --> 00:17:21,457
Kau pandai sekali mengabaikan orang.

